creational design patterns ka kaam ek hi hai:
👉 object kaise banega, kab banega, kitne banenge — is chaos ko control karna.

Creational Design Patterns wo patterns hote hain jo object creation mechanism ko control aur optimize karte hain, taaki system flexible, reusable aur loosely coupled rahe.

Core Idea (dil me bitha le)

3 basic sawaal solve karte hain:

Object kaise banega?
Kab banega?
Kitni baar banega?

Common Features
Object creation controlled hota hai
Loose coupling
Reusability
Flexibility increase hoti hai